Interface InteractionEvidenceSource<T extends InteractionEvidence>

  • All Superinterfaces:

    public interface InteractionEvidenceSource<T extends InteractionEvidence>
extends InteractionEvidenceStream<T>, InteractionSource<T>
    A Data source of interaction evidences. It gives full access to all the interactions using Iterator or the full collection. It can also give information about the size of the dataSource
